latestIgtvVideos.title: GAME
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
My first igtv had to be about something that I love - ACTING! 
if you want to become an actor or know anybody who would want to, please tag them and let them know and please contact us for more questions. 
We've got a great opportunity for you! with CINTAA being a part of GRME thanks to the captain of the ship @iamsiddharthsikka, and various production houses being associated with GAME, there's no way you can even think of ignoring it!

You can even leave your queries in the comment section below!
